304
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:51,680
Can you

305
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:52,480
give me a hand?

306
00:19:55,360 --> 00:19:57,420
It's too heavy. I can't lift it alone.

307
00:20:14,280 --> 00:20:15,080
Give me a hand.

308
00:20:16,360 --> 00:20:17,080
Take this?

309
00:20:17,800 --> 00:20:18,280
Yes.

310
00:20:25,400 --> 00:20:26,660
It's really too heavy.

311
00:20:27,720 --> 00:20:29,720
Can you help me carry it to my room?

312
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:32,160
Thank you.

313
00:20:33,160 --> 00:20:33,760
Okay.

314
00:20:40,760 --> 00:20:41,840
Right there.

315
00:20:42,480 --> 00:20:43,880
