368
00:22:29,400 --> 00:22:30,240
Bullets are coming!

369
00:22:30,240 --> 00:22:30,840
Incoming!

370
00:22:32,960 --> 00:22:33,960
Incoming!

371
00:22:34,800 --> 00:22:35,400
Right now,

372
00:22:35,440 --> 00:22:36,500
