373
00:22:36,560 --> 00:22:37,520
Time to eat.

374
00:22:39,040 --> 00:22:40,970
A big spin. That's enough, you two.

375
00:22:41,560 --> 00:22:43,480
If we miss the meal time,

376
00:22:43,640 --> 00:22:45,100
