377
00:22:45,120 --> 00:22:47,050
Alright, let's head back to Earth.

378
00:22:50,760 --> 00:22:51,400
Three.

379
00:22:52,600 --> 00:22:53,240
Five.

380
00:22:54,400 --> 00:22:55,040
Seven.

381
00:22:56,320 --> 00:22:56,920
Nine.

382
00:22:58,400 --> 00:23:00,000
Two.

383
00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:08,040
Three.

384
00:23:12,480 --> 00:23:13,880
Good performance today.

385
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:15,840
One for you.

386
00:23:15,840 --> 00:23:16,240
For you.

387
00:23:16,240 --> 00:23:17,960
Thank you.

388
00:23:18,960 --> 00:23:19,720
Feifei.

389
00:23:19,960 --> 00:23:21,360
