396
00:23:33,800 --> 00:23:34,240
No.

397
00:23:34,240 --> 00:23:35,770
My plane isn't this shabby.

398
00:23:35,840 --> 00:23:36,960
Look at this one.

399
00:23:38,360 --> 00:23:40,020
