400
00:23:43,800 --> 00:23:45,080
Awesome, right?

401
00:23:45,400 --> 00:23:45,760
Come on.

402
00:23:45,760 --> 00:23:46,720
Let's draw.

403
00:23:47,360 --> 00:23:49,000
Draw a little house.

404
00:23:53,440 --> 00:23:54,800
