425
00:24:29,680 --> 00:24:31,160
Me.

426
00:24:34,360 --> 00:24:35,160
Me.

427
00:24:35,280 --> 00:24:36,080
I want to sign up.

428
00:24:36,080 --> 00:24:37,040
I want to sing.

429
00:24:38,480 --> 00:24:38,840
