478
00:27:59,640 --> 00:28:00,440
Is it worth it?

479
00:28:00,560 --> 00:28:01,600
Is it worth it?

480
00:28:05,080 --> 00:28:06,080
Lin Jiaming.

481
00:28:07,920 --> 00:28:09,120
Let Brother Chao go.

482
00:28:09,440 --> 00:28:10,800
Let Zhang Chao go.

483
00:28:12,440 --> 00:28:13,760
Not worth it.

484
00:28:14,560 --> 00:28:16,320
Drinking like this is not worth it.

485
00:28:16,320 --> 00:28:18,000
Forget it, let's not drink.

486
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:19,160
Lin Jiaming,

487
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:20,200
let Zhang Chao go.

488
00:28:20,680 --> 00:28:22,000
Let Zhang Chao go.

489
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:23,040
Lin Jiaming,

490
00:28:23,240 --> 00:28:25,240
