494
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:30,720
Let's go.

495
00:28:31,160 --> 00:28:32,160
Let Zhang Chao go.

496
00:28:33,120 --> 00:28:34,800
Let Chao go.

497
00:28:35,040 --> 00:28:36,360
Lin Jiaming.

498
00:28:36,720 --> 00:28:37,840
Let Chao go.

499
00:28:37,840 --> 00:28:38,680
Don't be angry, Young Master Lin.

500
00:28:38,680 --> 00:28:39,400
Let's go, let's keep playing.

501
00:28:39,400 --> 00:28:39,880
Let's go.

502
00:28:39,880 --> 00:28:40,680
Keep playing.

503
00:28:40,880 --> 00:28:41,410
Let's go.

504
00:28:55,040 --> 00:28:57,760
Traces of existence.

505
00:28:59,120 --> 00:29:03,840
Forgotten memories are being awakened.

506
00:29:05,560 --> 00:29:06,800
The damp wind

507
00:29:06,800 --> 00:29:08,880
takes everything away,

508
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:13,040
along with your blank traces,

509
00:29:13,040 --> 00:29:16,040
and memories related to you.

510
00:29:17,960 --> 00:29:19,360
Sing to you?

511
00:29:20,240 --> 00:29:21,760
Young man,

512
00:29:21,760 --> 00:29:23,400
let me tell you a joke.

513
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:33,880
When we are all together.

514
00:29:33,880 --> 00:29:36,200
Together.

515
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:38,360
When we are all together.

516
00:29:38,360 --> 00:29:39,220
Hurry up, Chao.

517
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:42,720
When we are all together.

518
00:29:42,720 --> 00:29:43,480
Chao.

519
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:49,800
Fei.

520
00:29:51,520 --> 00:29:52,560
Come here.

521
00:29:56,000 --> 00:29:57,000
